\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
In this video, I present the changes made to the Nexus. <break time="1.0s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Instead of the Mothership, the Warp Prism can now be built directly at the Nexus, provided that a Cybernetics Core has been constructed. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
The Warp Prism can not only transport units and provide Psionic Matrix while in Phasing Mode, but it can also recharge shields in Phasing Mode, similar to the former Shield Battery. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
As a result, the Shield Battery has been removed from the game. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
In addition, the Psionic Matrix radius of the Warp Prism has been increased and now matches that of a Pylon, allowing Protoss structures to be powered more safely without having to place them too close to enemy attack range. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
In addition, the earlier availability of the Warp Prism is necessary to ensure that all races have equally fast options to leave or access islands. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
This change is very important to make much more diverse maps possible. <break time="1.0s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Let's move on to Strategic Recall. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Previously, Protoss armies often had to be teleported back to the Nexus, because Protoss units had few retreat options, and armies could only be moved between bases slowly. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Without Strategic Recall this often led to critical damage before reinforcements arrived and made comebacks difficult to achieve. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
However, since all units and structures now have more health and shields, most units deal less damage on average, and all races have received new or improved defensive tools, the early defensive option of Strategic Recall is no longer required. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Strategic Recall also feels very unfair for opponents, as even well-executed surrounds can be countered so easily. <break time="1.0s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Furthermore, many Protoss units now have enhanced retreat capabilities. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
These include earlier access to Warp Prisms with the Recharge Shields ability, Zealot's Charge, which can also be used for retreating, the double Blink for Stalkers, and Adept Shades that can instantly teleport to their shade via a button with a reduced cooldown, along with many other improvements. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
This means Protoss have more options to escape dangerous situations, but those options depend more on player skill. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
In addition, Protoss base defense has become significantly stronger overall, giving players far more time to reposition their armies for defense. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
These improved defensive options will be explored in greater detail in the upcoming videos. <break time="1.0s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Therefore, Strategic Recall has been removed from the Nexus and will return in a reworked form with the Mothership's replacement, the Arbiter, which can be built multiple times. <break time="1.0s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Additionally, Nexuses no longer share the cooldown of the Energy Recharge ability. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Each Nexus can now use its own Recharge independently, restoring 75 energy for 75 energy. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
This change was made to allow players to recharge more units without excessive clicking. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Each use provides enough energy for most abilities. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
While the ability itself is weaker due to the increased energy cost per point restored, it remains quite powerful thanks to the removed cooldown. <break time="1.0s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
With these changes, the Nexus now provides an important defensive unit as well as abilities, all of which can also be useful offensively in one way or another.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10
\~}
