\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
In this video, I showcase the changes made to the Immortal. <break time="1.0s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Previously, the Immortal lost its Hardened Shield because it was simply too powerful against Terran mech, especially Siege Tanks. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
While countering Siege Tanks has always been the Immortal's intended role, Hardened Shield did so too effectively. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
At the same time, the Immortal became too easily countered by units with low damage but very high attack speed, such as Zerglings or Marines. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
The current Barrier only lasts a few seconds, which makes it insufficiently impactful against heavily fortified defenses. <break time="1.0s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
To address this, the Barrier now blocks significantly more damage and lasts much longer, but it also has a noticeably longer cooldown before it can activate again. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
A new upgrade in the Robotics Bay can further extend its active duration, reducing the time it remains inactive. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
For better immersion, the visual appearance of the Barrier has also been updated to resemble the iconic shield from early concept art, fully enveloping the Immortal. <break time="1.0s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
These Barrier changes encourage opponents to try to trigger it early, forcing it to expire before Immortals reach their defensive lines. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Active scouting and brief hit-and-run engagements become more important to keep fortified positions secure over time. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
I see this as a fresh form of base defense, one that urges even heavily turtling players to move out of their bases occasionally in order to preserve them. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
At the same time, the improved Barrier gives attackers a temporary window to break through defenses if the opponent doesn't respond quickly enough. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
And beyond that, the stronger Barrier also gives Immortals more opportunities to retreat or be reinforced by supporting units.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10
\~}
