\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
In this video, I present the changes made to the Carrier. <break time="1.0s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Currently, a Carrier's Interceptors deal the same amount of damage against all unit types, and Carriers become very difficult to counter in large numbers. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Additionally, a Carrier starts with only 4 out of 8 Interceptors, meaning it isn't at full strength immediately after being built. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
This can be especially punishing in defensive situations where every unit counts, making Carriers less effective as comeback units despite their high cost. <break time="1.0s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
To give the Carrier clearer strengths and weaknesses, the Interceptors' base damage has been reduced but increased against armored units. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
To ensure the Carrier is immediately combat-ready, it now starts with 8 out of 8 Interceptors, which can also operate farther away from the Carrier, improving its potential to turn games around. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Interceptors now build faster, but they also cost more minerals. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
As a result, the Carrier becomes a strong siege unit, while being more effectively countered by non-armored units. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Losing large numbers of Interceptors becomes costly, making it more worthwhile to focus fire on them if the Carrier itself is out of range. <break time="1.0s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
Overall, Interceptors are now easier to counter and destroying them provides a greater reward because they are more expensive. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
At the same time, the Carrier is fully effective right away, can reposition more safely after launching its Interceptors, and can replenish them more quickly. <break time="0.4s" />}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10\loch
This makes the Carrier a strong siege option with clearer counterplay.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1031\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1031\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\hich\af6\loch\cs17\rtlch\af12 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\f4\dbch\af7\f6\dbch\af10
\~}
